pty input blocker error.\",\"Otherwise, return a passed status with the generated slug key placeholder.\"],\"exactOutputShapes\":{\"passed\":{\"status\":\"passed\",\"slugKeyPlaceholder\":\"<slug>\"},\"blockedEmptyInput\":{\"status\":\"blocked\",\"blocker\":\"empty_slug_input\"}},\"scopeBoundaries\":{\"allowedTargetOnly\":true,\"noTestMutation\":true,\"noDurableTruthClaim\":true,\"noExtraCriteria\":true},\"promotionPosture\":{\"projectionKind\":\"generated_tdd_proof_surface\",\"promotionStatus\":\"proof_surface_only\",\"notDurableProductTruth\":true,\"mustPromoteThrough\":\"semantic_operation_graph\"}},\"ambiguities\":[],\"assumptions\":[\"The input title is a string that may contain whitespace, punctuation, and mixed case characters.\",\"Unsupported punctuation characters are defined by the test intent and must be removed entirely.\",\"Empty input after trimming or after all transformations is considered invalid and must be blocked.\"],\"forbiddenClaims\":[\"No durable product truth is claimed.\",\"No test mutations are performed.\",\"No additional criteria beyond those specified are added.\"],\"acceptanceRequired\":true}"
